{"tid":334744,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"露鳥哥港鐵車廂自摸 女事主：做乜整濕我！","createTime":"2017-07-25T04:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T07:27:17.000Z","uid":525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d821605a4c6a76caa21c06420f4328bbb76315b4","tid":334744,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"港鐵金鐘站今早疑有變態四眼淫賊非禮女乘客，當場斷正被捕。讀者Jackson目擊事發經過，指出事發今早9時許，當時他正身處一列由尖沙嘴站開往金鐘站的港鐵列車內，差不多抵達金鐘站時，突然聽到一名女乘客舉起一名戴眼鏡青年的手，並高叫：「做乜露械，做乜整濕我？」<br />\n<br />\nJackson形容，車廂當時逼爆乘客，女事主站在靠近車門位置，色狼當場斷正後，便一直沒有反抗，「呆咗冇出聲」，而女事主的衣衫則確實濕了一片，面積約有兩個五毛子大小，但Jackson未有目睹色狼露械。車內一名女乘客協助女事主報警，另有一名男乘客亦協助看管色狼。當列車抵達金鐘站後，女事主一直捉著色狼的手不放，兩名熱心乘客則協助女事主將色狼帶至月台，其間色狼曾試圖逃走，但不成功。警員事後接報到場，將色狼拘捕蒙頭帶走調查。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170725&amp;guid=56998962&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170725%26guid%3D56998962%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=CtS3Nn%2BaoEd%2BECsNizbbEp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c7a0ff43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170725%26guid%3D56998962%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=fbd20a03\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170725&amp;guid=56998962&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"71c551c2e09611e8aa37d3ef735eb4870cba2594","tid":334744,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b94d8600efbd584b879b0265b29035e2770d316b","tid":334744,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉濕撚晒</blockquote><br />\n打錯字就自殺啦"},{"pid":"e66022ac6fb315acc901a9d6fe2b9524dd3ae29a","tid":334744,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"念力射精?"}]}